---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="About Shift at Midnight Compass — unofficial player status hub, not affiliated with Bun Muen or Kwalee.">
  <div class="panel hero" style="padding: 28px;">
    <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot accent"></span> Unofficial Player Hub</span>
    <h1>About Shift at Midnight Compass</h1>
  </div>

  <section class="panel section">
    <h2>What This Site Is</h2>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">Shift at Midnight Compass is an <strong>unofficial player status hub</strong>. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Bun Muen, Kwalee, or any platform.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">The site exists to help players find current, source-backed answers to early-stage questions about Shift at Midnight: demo availability, platform status, release-date conflict, and safe spoiler-free guidance. All facts are traced to official or platform sources.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="panel section">
    <h2>Scope</h2>
    <div class="can-cannot" style="margin-top: 14px;">
      <div class="can-card">
        <h3>This site does</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Track demo and platform availability from official sources</li>
          <li>Present release-date conflict as a timeline, not a final date</li>
          <li>Explain game premise and workflow shape without spoilers</li>
          <li>Label every source by type and confidence</li>
          <li>Clearly mark HOLD boundaries for unverified content</li>
          <li>Use no copyrighted images, screenshots, or media</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="cannot-card">
        <h3>This site does NOT</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Publish exact release dates without current official confirmation</li>
          <li>Copy walkthroughs, community guide content, or YouTube gameplay</li>
          <li>Include spoilers such as customer tells, routes, or endings</li>
          <li>Use Steam, Xbox, YouTube, or press images</li>
          <li>Sell anything or operate advertising</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="panel section">
    <h2>Evidence &amp; Updates</h2>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">This site's facts are versioned by date (currently evidence version 2026-07-06). When Steam, Xbox, or official sources change, the affected pages will be reviewed and updated. Use the contact page to report outdated information.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="panel section">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">To report an error, suggest a correction, or provide a verified official source, use the <a href="/contact/" style="color: var(--accent);">contact page</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Base>
